<body bgcolor="#FFFFE1" text="#000000">
<table width="600" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="4" align="center" bordercolor="#FF6600" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
  <tr>
    <td>
      <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
        <tr>
          <td>
            <div align="center"><%= image_tag 'newsletter_logo.gif', :alt => "Amani Children's Home" %></div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>
            <div align="center"><font face="Impact" size="5" color="#000099">Rescuing
              Children. Restoring Hope. Transforming Lives.</font></div>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      <hr>
      <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="2">
        <tr>
          <td valign="top">
            <p align="center" class="text"><font size="2" face="Comic Sans MS" class="text">Amani, located at the foot of Mt. Kilimanjaro, provides care and
education for nearly 300 street children and orphans in Amani's
home and in the local community.</font></p>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>

      <%= yield %>

      <hr>
      <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="2">
        <tr>
          <td><em class="text"><span class="mission">Amani Children&#8217;s Home is committed to reducing the number of children living on the streets in Tanzania by providing a nurturing place for homeless children to heal, grow, and learn. &nbsp;In addition to providing long-term care, Amani aims to reunite children with their relatives when possible and to equip their families with the tools they need to be self-sustainable. &nbsp;Amani is dedicated to creating a path for each child that leads to a future filled with hope.</span></em></td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      <hr>
      <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="2">
        <tr class="footer">
          <th width="70%" class="footer" scope="col"><font size="1" face="Tahoma" class="footer">If you'd like to unsubscribe from this quarterly newsletter, click <a href="../../leave.htm">here</a>.</font></th>
